OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,FA former lawyer serving a life
OL,7,Fsentence for murdering his wife and
OL,8,Fson in a case that gripped the US has
OL,9,Fhad his conviction overturned.
OL,11,FAlex Murdaugh, 57, now faces a re-
OL,12,Ftrial for the murders of his wife and
OL,13,Fhis 22-year-old son at their family
OL,14,Fhome in South Carolina after the court
OL,15,Fclerk appeared to unlawfully steer the
OL,16,Fjury to a guilty verdict during the
OL,17,Foriginal 2023 trial.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
