OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778702756
OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,F"Alex has said from day one that he
OL,7,Fdid not kill his wife and son. We look
OL,8,Fforward to a new trial," Murdaugh's
OL,9,Flawyers Dick Harpootlian and Jim
OL,10,FGriffin said in a joint statement.
OL,12,FIn their unanimous ruling on
OL,13,FWednesday, the South Carolina Supreme
OL,14,FCourt said the conduct by Colleton
OL,15,FCounty Clerk of Court Becky Hill
OL,16,F"egregiously attacked Murdaugh's
OL,17,Fcredibility" by suggesting to jurors
OL,18,Fhis testimony could not be trusted.
