OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,FA few jurors said Hill, assigned to
OL,7,Foversee the evidence and the jury
OL,8,Fduring the trial, told them to watch
OL,9,FMurdaugh's body language when he
OL,10,Ftestified in his own defence and to
OL,11,Fnot be fooled, confused or thrown off
OL,12,Fby what he might say.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
