OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778702756
OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,F"By urging the jurors not to be fooled
OL,7,For convinced by Murdaugh's defence,
OL,8,FHill essentially implored the jurors
OL,9,Fto find him guilty, the ultimate issue
OL,10,Fin the case," the justices wrote,
OL,11,Fadding that the comments insinuated
OL,12,Fthere was something unusual and
OL,13,Fsuspicious about his decision to
OL,14,Ftestify.
