OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,FHill was charged last May with
OL,7,Fperjury, obstruction of justice and
OL,8,Fmisconduct. The charges alleged she
OL,9,Fmade sealed evidence available to the
OL,10,Fmedia, lied under oath about doing so,
OL,11,Fand used her court position to promote
OL,12,Fher book about the trial.
OL,14,FShe pleaded guilty to the charges in
OL,15,FDecember 2025 and was sentenced to
OL,16,Fthree years of probation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
