PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778702756
OL,3,CUS lawyer found guilty of wife and
OL,4,Cson's murders has conviction overturned
OL,6,FThe court said Hill's motivation was
OL,7,Fthe "siren call of celebrity," and her
OL,8,Fgoal was to increase sales of her book
OL,9,Fon the trial called "Behind the Doors
OL,10,Fof Justice: The Murdaugh Murders."
OL,12,FIt was pulled from publication after
OL,13,Fplagiarism allegations were made.
OL,15,FProsecutors argued that the clerk's
OL,16,Fcomments were fleeting and the
OL,17,Fevidence against Murdaugh was
OL,18,Foverwhelming.
